            Beautiful watch, but that's all it is. If you're buying this as a health tracker, find something else. I did 35 minutes of cardio and it registered 1k steps (with other trackers this number would have been close to 4k) with 64 BPM (wayyyyy off) when I finished. I got a great night's sleep (almost 9 hours) and it tracked as 4.5 hours.

            Additional cons:
            Even on the lowest setting, this thing is bright! Not good for wearing at night since the screen wake also seems really sensitive and turns on with any slight movement.

            The weather feature is only in Celsius and there is no way to change it.

            Pros:
            The battery is great
            Display is nice and crisp
            Comes with a nice band-change kit and two decent bands
            Nice selection of watch faces
